{"tid":746852,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【打造大陸英雄】傳開拍《中國隊長》 羅素兄弟急澄清：與我們無關","createTime":"2018-07-18T02:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T13:26:19.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d229d87313eb43d36fff2ae90d05386a1c4035c3","tid":746852,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T02:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180717/large/1531818295_1afd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180717%2Flarge%2F1531818295_1afd.jpg&h=a04eabff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMarvel超級英雄電影大受歡迎，大陸都照辦煮碗打造咗一個叫「中國隊長」嘅英雄人物，要喺呢個超級英雄世界分一杯羹。<br />\n<br />\n早已有傳大陸片商欲將中國隊長拍成電影，近日內地就有消息話《中國隊長》已定明年五月開鏡，製作費高達3.6億人民幣，內容提到呢部係中國嘅首部超級英雄片，搵嚟《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》（Avengers: Infinity War）導演羅素兄弟（Anthony and Joe Russo）執導，故事講中國隊長於二戰期間被改造成戰爭武器，後來經歷數十年嘅冰封後被發現，故事同美國隊長簡直一模一樣。<br />\n<br />\n消息傳得似層層，羅素兄弟今日就透過微博澄清，話從來冇聽過呢個計劃，拍《中國隊長》與佢哋無關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180717/58453214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180717%2F58453214&d=S6G0BtnUd%2F2LN8rd4i%2FdHzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=fa97cd56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180717%2F58453214&h=a44ffe48\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180717/58453214</a>"},{"pid":"9193093a5ee5ac7af736d09fa460530be7887367","tid":746852,"uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T02:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-15317073853472.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-15317073853472.jpg&h=d6d34dcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-15317073860677.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-15317073860677.jpg&h=74ba2764&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"600545bdf6b60158c60a2365db54d28536e40b2e","tid":746852,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T02:28:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.xingyule.com/detail/show/id/39450.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xingyule.com%2Fdetail%2Fshow%2Fid%2F39450.html&d=S6G0BtnUd%2F2LN8rd4i%2FdHzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=4e8b3466\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.xingyule.com/detail/show/id/39450.html</a><br />\n<br />\n羅素兄弟都幫吳京打造左中國超級英雄<br />\n無需要重複自己"},{"pid":"7ce07985cac56656814300e408522e17a0403080","tid":746852,"uid":52511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:21:39.000Z","msg":"羅素兄弟：企開d啦 屌你老母.jpg"},{"pid":"5b70058b3790544dc1b2e11c067a2d223860a90b","tid":746852,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:26:19.000Z","msg":"China captain will replace US captain in 2025"}]}